<div class="app-card-ccontainer">
  <div class="card card-font-color">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "picture_of_me.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills ">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4> <%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progress-bar"
                  aria-valurnow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Hello, my name is Rustin Player and Iâ€™m a full stack developer. I have an interest in technology, mathematics, and music, as well as an abiding passion for learning and puzzles. My current interests lie in machine learning, algorithms, and computer security. </p>
        <p></p>
        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="true"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Jobs
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="true"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block collapse-background">
              Cheese Cake Factory  Oct - Nov 2013
            </div>                       
          </div>
          
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jordan High School: 2013
            </div>            
            <div class="card card-block">
              Salt Lake Community College: 2016
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bottega
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Univsersity of Utah: Continuing Education
            </div>           
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

